from sklearn.decomposition import KernelPCA
from sklearn.model_selection import GridSearchCV
from sklearn.metrics import mean_squared_error
In [22]:
# scorer for grid search
def my_scorer(estimator, X, y=None):
    X_reduced = estimator.transform(X)
    X_preimage = estimator.inverse_transform(X_reduced)
    return -1 * mean_squared_error(X, X_preimage)

# Seaborn 尺寸、顏色
sns.set_color_codes("pastel")
sns.set(rc={'figure.figsize':(120,90)})
# Seaborn 中文設定
import seaborn as sns
sns.set(font=['sans-serif'])
sns.set_style("darkgrid",{"font.sans-serif":['Microsoft JhengHei']})

# prepare output text
uname['output'] = uname['school_name_abbr'] + uname['department_name_abbr']
output = dep_category_map.merge(uname.loc[:,['department_id','output']], 
                       on='department_id', how='inner')

final_plot = sns.scatterplot(x=X_tsne_Jaccard[:,0],
                             y=X_tsne_Jaccard[:,1],
                             hue=dep_category_map.iloc[:,1],
                             y_jitter=True)

for line in range(0,X_tsne_Jaccard.shape[0]):
     final_plot.text(X_tsne_Jaccard[line,0]+0.2,
                     X_tsne_Jaccard[line,1],
                     output.iloc[line,-1],
                     horizontalalignment='left',
                     fontsize=10,
                     color='gray', weight='semibold')
plt.savefig('output.png')
plt.close()
